This is my new surf map,
it's a very dark map, I hope you can see everything ;), if not use the flashlight.

you spawn with a dual elite

There are weapon boxes with m4a1(on the ct spawn), ak 47(on the t spawn), p90, mp5, m3, xm1014, sg-550, sg-1, he, awp and deagle

a special of the map are the iris doors

please rate and report bugs

have fun!
